# Summary
The Anomaly + Forecast feature in Amplitude identifies statistically significant deviations in metrics based on historical data, using a Prophet-based algorithm with three modes (agile, robust, custom) and configurable confidence intervals, while also offering future metric projections and automated project alerts for Growth and Enterprise plan users.

